               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Ḥaz̤arāt al-quds by Badr al-Dīn ibn Ibrāhīm Sihrindī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85089787" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_630-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Substantive Naqshbandī Sufi hagiographical collection by 
                <persName key="viaf_288094039" role="aut">Badr al-Dīn ibn Ibrāhīm Sirhindī</persName> (of present Sirhind), dealing with the virtues of important figures from the 
                <persName key="viaf_97606468" role="subject">Caliph Abū Bakr</persName> to the formation of the Mujaddidī branch of the Naqshbandīyah silsilah in India, under the Mujaddid-i alf-i s̲ānī, 
                <persName key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164657162.0x000001 viaf_32839461" role="subject">Shaykh Aḥmad ibn ʿAbd al-Aḥad ibn Zayn al-ʿĀbidīn al-Fārūqī al-Kābulī al-Naqshbandī</persName>(d. 1034/1624).
                        </p>
                        <p>Colophon not dated (f. 183v): completed by 
                <persName key="person_f8139" role="scr">Muḥammad Zamān the kātib</persName>(scribe).
                        </p>
                        <p>Neat scribal naskh throughout.</p>
                        <p>Annotations in margins.</p>
                        <p>Foliation in pencil throughout.</p>
                        <p>Rebound in IOL red half leather binding, stamp dated 15 Jul 1966.</p>
                        <p>Folios rebound and remounted onto paper apertures; wormholes, stains, smudging, creasing.</p>
                     </note>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21717">Ḥaz̤arāt al-quds</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_21717">حضراة القدس</title>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_288094039">Badr al-Dīn ibn Ibrāhīm Sihrindī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="viaf_288094039">بدر الدّين ابن ابراهيم سهرندى</persName>
